  "body": "We don't currently implement AuRa's custom blockGasLimitContract, but Chiado and other Gnosis test networks use it (search for `BlockGasLimitContractTransitions`). Because of this the following issue occurred on gnosis_withdrawals_devnet_2 (PR #7150):\r\n```\r\n[DBUG] [03-21|09:24:12.652] [downloader] Verification failed for header hash=0xc693c0481d4c890d7a4d252171f23e035704b44d2169a176b2ca34c95664707d height=1 err=\"invalid gas limit: have 12500000, want 10000000 +-= 9764\"\r\n```",
